  "privacy_body": "SeekerCraft respects your privacy.\n\nWHAT WE COLLECT\n• Wallet address (public key only — never private keys)\n• Game scores, achievements, levels you create\n• Play counts and ratings\n\nHOW WE USE IT\nYour wallet address is used as a unique identifier for the leaderboard and achievement system. We never sell your data to third parties.\n\nDATA STORAGE\nAll data is stored securely on Google Firebase (USA). Blockchain transactions are public by design and visible on Solana explorers.\n\nYOUR RIGHTS\nYou can disconnect your wallet at any time from the Wallet tab. This removes your local session.\n\nSECURITY\nWe never request, store or have access to your private keys or seed phrases. All Solana transactions are signed exclusively by your wallet app.\n\nCONTACT\nFor privacy questions, contact us via X (@SeekerCraftApp).\n\nLast updated: February 2026",

